{You have a perfect 2\D opening except for one thing. Well, except for four things really, those four \Ss. So you pass. Then partner opens 1\S.  

Well, we have passed out of the realm of Weak Twos and into Major Suit Raises! No problem, it's all Bridge. Youmake a limit raise of 3\S and partner bids 4\S.}

